[This is the 1st report by the CHP discussing avian influenza in humans since a report from 9 Mar 2015 of a cumulative 59 cases with onset dates from 21 Jan to 25 Feb 2015 and a report on an imported case of H5N1 (See ProMED-mail post Avian influenza, human (69): China H7N9 20150312.3225992 and Avian influenza, human (70): China (SC) H5N1 20150313.3228528, respectively). It is not clear whether cases have not been occurring or are not being reported. If anyone knowledgeable has information on the sudden silence we are encountering, we would be grateful.

The provinces of China may be viewed at http://www.china-mike.com/china-travel-tips/tourist-maps/china-provinces-map.

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=3247717,155. - Mod.LK]
